description:
Between the Prince of Persia: The Lost Crown team being moved onto other projects, last-minute changes to the release of Assassin's Creed Shadows, and no news on games like the Splinter Cell Remake and Beyond Good and Evil, we ask: what the hell is going on with Ubisoft?

#gaming #ubisoft  #acshadows  #princeofpersia  #gamespot
title: What The Hell Is Going On With Ubisoft? | Spot On

description: Debuting in Sonic Adventure 2, Shadow the Hedgehog has quickly become one of the most popular characters in the Sonic Universe. From his creation on the ARK as the "Ultimate Lifeform" to his relationship with Maria and ongoing appearances in all of Sonic Media, this is the origin of Shadow the Hedgehog.
title: Who Is Shadow the Hedgehog - Sonic X Shadow Generations
